# gdrv.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 

### Description

gdrv.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: 613b8509-18c0-4720-b489-736776b6713e
- **Created**: 2023-05-06
- **Author**: Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create gdrv.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\gdrv.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start gdrv.sys
```

|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
